{
  "chapter": 100,
  "chapter_summary": "第一百回 双骄再聚。苏樱劝铁萍姑利用自身魅力吸引小鱼儿，铁萍姑感激离去。小鱼儿与苏樱在洞中斗嘴，苏樱透露花无缺已去找铁心兰，且铁心兰正在魏无牙的老鼠洞中。小鱼儿大怒，正要对苏樱动手时，花无缺意外出现。邀月宫主现身，小鱼儿首次见到其真容——冷若冰霜却美得令人不敢直视。铁心兰夹在小鱼儿与花无缺之间左右为难。邀月宫主给小鱼儿三个时辰休息，小鱼儿故意提及铜先生之事试探花无缺。苏樱与铁心兰推心置腹，两个女子坦诚面对对小鱼儿的感情，苏樱表示不会放弃小鱼儿，但要让他自己选择。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我懂了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "很好，只要你照着我的话去做，不怕他不来找你，等他来找你的时候，就是你出气的时候到了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但是我……我现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你觉得自己现在孤零零的一个人，身无长物，又没有倚靠，是以心里有些害怕，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你莫忘了，你是个很美丽、很动人的女孩子，年纪又轻，这已经是女人最大的财产了。就凭这样，你就可以将世上大多数男人摆在你的手心里；就凭这些，你无论走到哪都可以抬起头来的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你把别人都弄走了，自己为什么不走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "走？我为什么要走？这地方不是很舒服么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "求求你，你快走吧！我现在一个头已经有别人三个那么大了，你若再不走，我说不定马上就要发疯。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若是看到我就生气，不会自己走么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好，小丫头，我服了你了。我从生下来到现在，还没有一个人让我这样生气过，我总算遇见了对手。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "就算发霉了又有什么关系，你难道还想带出去么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你以为移花宫主立刻就能将花无缺找来么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你知道江玉郎是在骗我，那么你一定见过了花无缺，对不对？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我的确见过了他，也知道他到什么地方去了，但是，现在我却不能告诉你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你为什么不能告诉我？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "因为我怕你生气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "若生气我就是王八蛋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "因为你绝不会变成王八蛋的，任何人都不会忽然变成王八蛋，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好，我若生气，你叫我干什么，我就干什么！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，我告诉你。花无缺现在去找铁心兰去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他去找铁心兰去了？他怎会知道铁心兰在哪里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我告诉他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你告诉他的？你怎会知道铁心兰在哪里？怎会认得她的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我已经和她结拜为异姓姐妹，你难道不知道么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你是不是已有很久没见过铁心兰了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道，这两个月来，铁心兰一直和花无缺在一起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他们能在一起倒不错，我本来一直在担心着她，现在可放心了，我知道花无缺一直对她很好的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你为何不问我铁心兰现在在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你总不会将她送到那老鼠洞里去吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她正是在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你这死丫头，你怎么能将她送到那里去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她是我的姐妹，在那地方正安全得很，谁也不会欺负她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但花无缺此番去找她，那大老鼠怎会放过花无缺，你……你这不是在害人么，我……我……我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "今天我若不狠狠揍你一顿，实在对不起他们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说过不生气的，男子汉大丈夫，怎么能在我这种小丫头面前食言背信。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "其实你也不用着急，花无缺死不了的，何况，他一心要杀死你，本来就不能算是你的朋友，他若不能来，你岂非也用不着为难了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你以为你这是在帮我的忙？以为他死了我一定很开心？老实告诉你，他若真被魏无牙害死了，我就……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你在哪里，你听得到我说话么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，我就在这里。你放条绳子下来，我就可以上去了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好小子，两个月没见，我们都没有变。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你在下面我看不见你，你快上来吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姓苏的小丫头，你现在还不想走么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你一个人走吧，我不想看见你被人杀死的样子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你不想看，我就偏要你看，不想走，我就偏要你走，看你有什么法子反抗我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你敢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你送来的东西都不错，只可惜没有辣椒，下次你若再请我吃饭，可千万不能忘记我喜欢吃辣的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "现在我再给你三个时辰，你在三个时辰内，不妨调息运气，养精蓄锐，但却不准离开这里！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "移花宫主果然不愧为移花宫主，丝毫不肯占人便宜，知道我累了，就让我先休息休息。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "无缺，你随我来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我想和花无缺说两句话，行不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "为什么不行，你难道怕我告诉他你就是铜先生？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好久不见，你好么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "三个时辰并不长，你还是好生歇歇吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你瞧见铁心兰了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你没有看见我方才已经和她打过招呼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但是她……她实在可怜得很，你实在应该去安慰安慰她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我为什么要过去安慰她？她为什么不能过来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她现在的确很为难……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "她为难，我就不为难么？何况，她为难也是她自己找的，谁叫她站在那边不肯过来？又没有钉子钉住了她的脚。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你既然不肯过去，我就过去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你会不会读唇语？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我现在若能听出移花宫主在对花无缺说什么，那就好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就算听不见，也应该想像得到的，她现在还不是在告诉花无缺，要用什么法子才能杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "方才我在洞里时，花无缺还和我有说有笑的，但等我出来他竟不理我了，简直连看都没有看我一眼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若在移花宫长大，你见了移花宫主，也会变得没主意的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这样看来，'恶人谷'反而比'移花宫'好得多了，恶人谷里的至少还是人，移花宫却只是一群活鬼，一群行尸走肉。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你歇歇吧，我过去说两句话就回来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你为什么一定要过去？我现在也不好受，你为什么不在这里陪着我？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道不想知道，她和花无缺两人是如何从那老鼠洞里出来的么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你在生我的气？是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你用不着难过，我若知道你就是我情敌，我也不会对你说真话的！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我真没想到你是这样的女孩子，我现在只希望你是个又凶又狠又狡猾的女人，那样我心里就会好受得多了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "可是无论怎样，你也不会为我放弃小鱼儿的，是么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不错，我不会为了你放弃他的，只因我若放弃了他，也许反而会令你更为难，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我实在不该对你说那句话的，小鱼儿也许根本就没有将我放在心上，也许只有你才配得上他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "小鱼儿并没有忘记你，他若真的未将你放在心上，现在早已走过来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你……你为什么要告诉我？你为什么不让我死了这条心？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这也许是因为我太想得到小鱼儿了，所以才不愿让他以后恨我，我要让他自己选择，他喜欢的若是你，我就算杀了你，也没有用的。",
      "tone": "凄然",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你可瞧见了我义父么？他是不是长得很可怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我没有瞧见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    }
  ],
